arStrings.szText: Confessor Prava received a report about a horned woman from a Pale Knight named Vigo who is stationed in Yelesna. I need to speak to him and verify whether the woman was Lilith.
Vigo, the Pale Knight who sent Confessor Prava the report about the horned woman, is posted at the Old Mine Camp near Yelesna. I will speak to him there.
Vigo, Neyrelle, and I must pursue Lilith and Neyrelle's mother, Vhenard, into the depths of the Condemned Mines.
